_source.productDescription:
Celebrate the beginning of the Festive Season! 

Join in as Bulcock Street comes alive for a twilight evening full of activities. Spanning the length of Bulcock Street in Caloundra, the night market will showcase the food and artesian stalls you know and love, entertainment galore, plus some special surprises.

Caloundra Christmas Street Party: A free event â€“ Family fun not to be missed! 

Local performances
Christmas Twilight Market
Night retail - extended trade just for Christmas!
Live music
Kids activities and Free Kids Ride
Free Kids face painting
Local cuisine
Plus lots more

Follow Uncover Caloundra on socials for more announcements!

This project is a collaborative effort between Downtown Caloundra Taskforce, Sunshine Coast Council, Caloundra Chamber of Commerce and the Caloundra Business Alliance: Funded by the Caloundra CBD Regulated Parking Fund.
_source.productShortDescription: Join in as Bulcock Street comes alive for a twilight evening full of activities.

_source.productDescription:
Witness the Joscho Stephan Trio, hailed as one of the most exciting ensembles in the acoustic guitar scene today. Led by the masterful playing of Joscho Stephan, joined by Sven Jungbeck (guitar) and Volker Kamp (double bass), they breathe fresh life into the classic gypsy swing style pioneered by Django Reinhardt. Their live performances reveal a mesmerizing synergy and technical brilliance that have captivated audiences and critics alike.

As seasoned festival favorites, the Joscho Stephan Trio has wowed crowds at prestigious events such as Leverkusener Jazz Tage and Rheingau Music Festival, in addition to selling out concert halls across Germany. Their music has already captured hearts in Italy, Poland, USA, and Spain, and soon they'll be bringing their extraordinary performances to audiences in Australia.

Meanwhile, Joscho's YouTube channelâ€”amassing nearly 40 million viewsâ€”is a testament to the widespread devotion of fans around the globe.

At the heart of the trio's success is their fearless musical innovation. While they reverently rework timeless jazz standards, they also infuse their own compositions with influences spanning Latin, classical, pop, and rockâ€”making every set a dynamic feast for the ears.

_source.productName: Five Nights at Freddy's 2 - Fright Night Friday at Dendy Cinemas Coorparoo
_source.productDescription:
Could you survive five nights? 

Experience the next blood-chilling chapter of animatronic terror with a Stone & Wood beer on arrival!

One year has passed since the supernatural nightmare at Freddy Fazbear's Pizza. Former security guard Mike has kept the truth from his 11-year-old sister, Abby, concerning the fate of her animatronic friends. When Abby sneaks out to reconnect with Freddy, Bonnie, Chica and Foxy, she sets into motion a terrifying series of events that reveal dark secrets about the true origin of Freddy's.

_source.productName: Morning Melodies - Darren Coggan: Home For Christmas
_source.productDescription:
Seasonâ€™s greetings music lovers, time to â€œDeck the shed with bits of wattleâ€ and join award winning performer, Darren Coggan, as he celebrates the joy of being Home For Christmas through a collection of songs and stories that embrace the festive spirit of Christmas in Australia.

Darren Coggan is one of Australiaâ€™s most exciting and diverse artists, a masterful storyteller with a knack of weaving fascinating and perceptive tales through his songs. Darren has forged a unique, diverse career that has seen him embrace the Australian Country Music, Musical Theatre and Television industries with aplomb. His touring productions celebrating the songbooks of John Denver, James Taylor and his critically acclaimed portrait of Cat Stevens have inspired audiences in the grandest theatres across the globe including sell out seasons at the Sydney Opera House Concert Hall, Glasgow Royal Concert Hall and Liverpool Philharmonic.

Home For Christmas is a fun and engaging performance full of laughter and sing-along songs that promises to be the gift of the season.

_source.productDescription:
Mark your advent calendars because it's time for a mistle-toast at West End's magical Christmas Twilight Market! 

Visit the Facebook event page for your chance to win a free dinner for four at the West End Christmas Twilight Market. Come dance under the West End Christmas trees, and enjoy some of the best eats, treats and beats South East Queensland has to offer.

Get ready to dance beneath the twinkling West End Christmas trees and soak up the festive vibes with the best eats, treats, and beats in South East Queensland. Sip something merry at the twilight pop-up bar, but don't get your tinsel in a tangle â€” or you might end up on Santa's naughty list before you grab that selfie with the big man himself! 

Tick off your Christmas shopping with over 150 festive stalls, and be dazzled by roving stilt walkers, Nutcrackers, and a kids' disco sure to melt even the grinchiest hearts faster than a snowman in the Queensland sun.

_source.productName: Tom Curtain's Here's to You Tour - Boonah
_source.productDescription:
Nationally acclaimed singer-songwriter Tom Curtain is again hitting the road, touring his national award-winning outback show 'Katherine Outback Experience' and live music event with fellow singer songwriters Laura Frank, Chris Matthews and Melanie Gray. 

The family-friendly event includes an hour Katherine Outback Experience show of real horse training and working dog demonstrations including hands-on fun for the kids. Two hours of live music by Tom Curtain, Laura Frank, Chris Matthews and Melanie Gray.

Tom is passionate about bringing his show to towns and communities that are often overlooked on the entertainment trail. He is also an official ambassador of Dollys Dream and Farm Angels.
_source.productShortDescription: Nationally acclaimed singer songwriter Tom Curtain is again hitting the road, touring his national award winning outback show 'Katherine Outback Experience' and live music event.

productComments.commentText:
Nationally acclaimed singer-songwriter Tom Curtain is again hitting the road, touring his national award-winning outback show 'Katherine Outback Experience' and live music event with fellow singer songwriters Laura Frank, Chris Matthews and Melanie Gray. 

The family-friendly event includes an hour Katherine Outback Experience show of real horse training and working dog demonstrations including hands-on fun for the kids. Two hours of live music by Tom Curtain, Laura Frank, Chris Matthews and Melanie Gray.

Tom is passionate about bringing his show to towns and communities that are often overlooked on the entertainment trail. He is also an official ambassador of Dollys Dream and Farm Angels.

Tom est passionnÃ© par l'idÃ©e de faire dÃ©couvrir son spectacle aux villes et communautÃ©s souvent oubliÃ©es du monde du divertissement. Il est Ã©galement ambassadeur officiel de Dollys Dream et de Farm Angels.

Il cantautore di fama nazionale Tom Curtain Ã¨ di nuovo in tournÃ©e con il suo spettacolo nell'outback, vincitore di un premio nazionale "Katherine Outback Experience", e un evento musicale dal vivo con i cantautori Laura Frank, Chris Matthews e Melanie Gray.

L'evento, adatto alle famiglie, include un'ora di spettacolo "Katherine Outback Experience", con addestramento di cavalli e dimostrazioni di cani da lavoro, oltre a momenti di divertimento per i bambini. Due ore di musica dal vivo con Tom Curtain, Laura Frank, Chris Matthews e Melanie Gray.

Tom porta con passione il suo spettacolo in cittÃ  e comunitÃ  spesso trascurate nel panorama dell'intrattenimento. Ãˆ anche ambasciatore ufficiale di Dollys Dream e Farm Angels.

Penyanyi-penulis lagu ternama nasional, Tom Curtain, kembali beraksi, menggelar tur peraih penghargaan nasional untuk pertunjukan pedalamannya, 'Katherine Outback Experience', dan acara musik langsung bersama rekan-rekan penyanyi dan penulis lagunya, Laura Frank, Chris Matthews, dan Melanie Gray.

Acara ramah keluarga ini mencakup pertunjukan Katherine Outback Experience selama satu jam, yang menampilkan pelatihan kuda sungguhan dan demonstrasi anjing pekerja, termasuk keseruan langsung untuk anak-anak. Dua jam musik langsung akan dibawakan oleh Tom Curtain, Laura Frank, Chris Matthews, dan Melanie Gray.

Tom sangat antusias untuk membawa pertunjukannya ke kota-kota dan komunitas yang seringkali terabaikan dalam dunia hiburan. Ia juga merupakan duta resmi Dollys Dream dan Farm Angels.

_source.productDescription:
Could you survive five nights? 

Experience the next blood-chilling chapter of animatronic terror with a Stone & Wood beer on arrival!

One year has passed since the supernatural nightmare at Freddy Fazbear's Pizza. Former security guard Mike has kept the truth from his 11-year-old sister, Abby, concerning the fate of her animatronic friends. When Abby sneaks out to reconnect with Freddy, Bonnie, Chica and Foxy, she sets into motion a terrifying series of events that reveal dark secrets about the true origin of Freddy's.

_source.productDescription:
The Number One Ladies Only Sing and Dance Along Party!

Craving a much-needed girls' night out? Or maybe you're ready to experience the magic of a room full of women singing, dancing, and lifting each other up? Then Sing Out Sister is the excuse you've been waiting for!

This high energy, hit event series has been lighting up venues all over Australia and is designed especially for women to laugh and let loose in a zero judgement environment, surrounded by a tribe of new friends and inspiring sisters. 

You can sit, skip, dance, lean, or just boogie in your seat to all the classic anthems like Dancing Queen, Man I feel Like A Woman, I Will Survive, Living On a Prayer, Girls Just Wanna Have Fun and so many more! 

With all the lyrics on the big screen, plus games, prizes, costumes (encouraged) and so many Insta worthy moments, this really is the ultimate night out for you and your bestie, work wife, mothers, aunties, soul sisters and daughters. Whether you're the diva of the group or just love shouting the chorus, this is an evening of fun you won't want to miss. 

Ready to feel the power of connection, music and sisterhood? Then call your gal pals and get your Sing Out Sister tickets sorted - they won't last long!
_source.productShortDescription: The Number One Ladies Only Sing and Dance Along Party!

Pesta Bernyanyi dan Berdansa Nomor Satu Khusus Wanita!

Ingin menikmati malam khusus wanita? Atau mungkin Anda siap merasakan keajaiban ruangan yang penuh dengan wanita bernyanyi, menari, dan saling mendukung? Maka Sing Out Sister adalah alasan yang Anda tunggu-tunggu!

Rangkaian acara yang meriah dan penuh energi ini telah memeriahkan berbagai tempat di seluruh Australia dan dirancang khusus bagi para wanita untuk tertawa dan bergembira dalam suasana tanpa penghakiman, dikelilingi oleh teman-teman baru dan saudari-saudari yang menginspirasi.

Anda dapat duduk, melompat-lompat, menari, bersandar, atau sekadar bergoyang di tempat duduk Anda mengikuti semua lagu kebangsaan klasik seperti Dancing Queen, Man I feel Like A Woman, I Will Survive, Living On a Prayer, Girls Just Wanna Have Fun, dan masih banyak lagi!

Dengan semua lirik di layar lebar, ditambah permainan, hadiah, kostum (disarankan) dan begitu banyak momen yang layak diunggah ke Instagram, ini benar-benar malam terbaik untuk Anda dan sahabat, istri kantor, ibu, bibi, saudari, dan putri tercinta. Entah Anda seorang diva di grup atau hanya suka menyanyikan bagian reff, ini adalah malam penuh keseruan yang sayang untuk dilewatkan.

Siap merasakan kekuatan koneksi, musik, dan persaudaraan? Kalau begitu, hubungi teman-teman perempuan Anda dan pesan tiket Sing Out Sister Anda - tiketnya tidak akan lama lagi!

_source.productDescription:
Grab your mates, enemies, neighbours, or family and get ready for a night of side-splitting laughter! If you like the hit TV show 'Whose Line is it Anyway?', you'll love this style of improvised comedy even more in person at Currumbin Hotel (upstairs)! Sit back, have a laugh, have a wine/beer and dinner, and you may even win a free drink! With your suggestions, our talented improvisers create hilarious sketches on the spot!

Improv Comedy FriYAY is a family-friendly show by Blah Blah Blah Improv, the Gold Coast's premier improv company. It is the only comedy night on the Gold Coast where you can bring the kids AND have a drink!

This is what the reviewers say: "Big laughs! Highly enjoyable, an impressive bit of family-friendly comedy!"â€” Theatre Haus

_source.productDescription:
Alan Davies thinks he's Marty McFly but he's older than Doc Brown. He spends more time in the pharmacy than the gym. Subject to relentless eye rolls from his kids. What is he? A late middle-aged stand up on tour for the first time in a decade. Funnier than ever, he says.

Davies is a staple of British television, known for his performance as the eponymous hero of David Renwick's hugely popular, long-running television series Jonathan Creek, and as a permanent panelist on QI. His talk show, Alan Davies: As Yet Untitled, recently reached its seventh season. He is also one of the UK's best-loved comedians. His stand-up show Urban Trauma ran in London's West End and Life is Pain and Little Victories sold out in venues across Australia and the UK. His second memoir, Just Ignore Him was published in 2020 and the third instalment will be published later this year.
_source.productShortDescription: Alan Davies thinks he's Marty McFly but he's older than Doc Brown. He spends more time in the pharmacy than the gym.

productComments.commentText:
Alan Davies thinks he's Marty McFly but he's older than Doc Brown. He spends more time in the pharmacy than the gym. Subject to relentless eye rolls from his kids. What is he? A late middle-aged stand up on tour for the first time in a decade. Funnier than ever, he says.

Davies is a staple of British television, known for his performance as the eponymous hero of David Renwick's hugely popular, long-running television series Jonathan Creek, and as a permanent panelist on QI. His talk show, Alan Davies: As Yet Untitled, recently reached its seventh season. He is also one of the UK's best-loved comedians. His stand-up show Urban Trauma ran in London's West End and Life is Pain and Little Victories sold out in venues across Australia and the UK. His second memoir, Just Ignore Him was published in 2020 and the third instalment will be published later this year.

Alan Davies mengira dirinya Marty McFly, tetapi dia lebih tua dari Doc Brown. Dia menghabiskan lebih banyak waktu di apotek daripada di pusat kebugaran. Anak-anaknya terus-menerus memutar mata. Siapa dia? Seorang pelawak setengah baya yang sedang tur untuk pertama kalinya dalam satu dekade. Lebih lucu dari sebelumnya, katanya.

Davies adalah bintang utama televisi Inggris, dikenal karena penampilannya sebagai pahlawan yang namanya sama dalam serial televisi David Renwick yang sangat populer dan telah lama tayang, Jonathan Creek, dan sebagai panelis tetap di QI. Acara bincang-bincangnya, Alan Davies: As Yet Untitled, baru-baru ini mencapai musim ketujuh. Dia juga salah satu komedian paling dicintai di Inggris. Acaranya, Urban Trauma, ditayangkan di West End London dan Life is Pain dan Little Victories terjual habis di berbagai tempat di Australia dan Inggris. This live performance will showcase the greatest hits (and costumes) from both artists with The David Bowie Show opening the night with songs such as Letâ€™s Dance, Heroâ€™s, Space Oddity, Changes, Ashes to Ashes, China Girl and many more.

Queen & David Bowie adalah ikon musik yang bertemu pada tahun 1980-an saat mereka berkolaborasi dalam lagu hit "Under Pressure"

Setelah Tur Asia 2024 "Under Pressure" mempertemukan dua Pertunjukan Penghormatan paling dicari di Australia - The Killer Queen Experience dan The David Bowie Show, yang dibintangi John Blunt yang terkenal di seluruh dunia karena kemiripannya dengan Freddie Mercury dan Wayne Vitale yang dikenal sebagai pengisi suara David Bowie. 

Pertunjukan langsung ini akan menampilkan hits terhebat (dan kostum) dari kedua artis dengan The David Bowie Show membuka malam dengan lagu-lagu seperti Let's Dance, Hero's, Space Oddity, Changes, Ashes to Ashes, China Girl, dan masih banyak lagi. 

Killer Queen akan memberikan Experience lengkap dengan membawakan semua hits terhebat Queen termasuk - Bohemian Rhapsody, We Will Rock You, We Are the Champions, Somebody to Love, Radio Ga Ga, Another One Bites the Dust, dan banyak lagi dalam pertunjukan berdurasi 2 jam ini yang tidak boleh dilewatkan.

_source.productName: Dead Head Redemption, Lewin Grimley & the Broken Strings and Damien J Johnson
_source.productDescription:
They have a genre-tastic tasting plate here at Banshees Bar & Artspace!

Local legends the Damien J Johnson trio open with their country crowd-whippers and dusty darkwave, hot off their latest single Away From You. 

Next up are gothic gurus Lewin Grimley & The Broken Strings, their virtuosic guitar lines shading melancholy meanderings through pain, loss, and a bright glimpse of hope. 

And closing out the evening all the way from the swampy north of Meanjin, Dead Head Redemption bring their dirgey doomgrass and outlaw rock n' roll to Banshees for the first time!

Come thunder come hail we'll be the home of Ipswich live music as always!

Mereka punya hidangan pencicipan yang fantastis di Banshees Bar & Artspace!

Trio legenda lokal, Damien J Johnson, membuka dengan lagu-lagu country mereka yang memukau penonton dan darkwave yang bernuansa debu, yang baru saja dirilis untuk single terbaru mereka, Away From You.

Selanjutnya adalah para guru gothic, Lewin Grimley & The Broken Strings, dengan alunan gitar virtuoso mereka yang membayangi liku-liku melankolis di antara rasa sakit, kehilangan, dan secercah harapan.

Dan menutup malam dari utara Meanjin yang berawa, Dead Head Redemption membawakan musik doomgrass yang memilukan dan rock n' roll outlaw mereka ke Banshees untuk pertama kalinya!

Ayo, ayo, kita akan menjadi tuan rumah musik live Ipswich seperti biasa!

_source.productDescription:
Floating through space, the interstellar pansexual humanoid Hairy Soul Man hears a cry. The cry of a collective unconsciousness yearning for change. For an awakening. Riding his unstoppable Love Meteor, Hairy Soul Man crashes into earth, sharing ways to better humanity and looking fantastic while doing so.

Come one and all to celebrate the launch of this brand new five-part comedy musical sketch series. With a sneak preview of the first few episodes and a live performance from Hairy Soul Man backed by his salacious live band. Everyone is welcome on the Love Meteor
_source.productShortDescription: Floating through space, the interstellar pansexual humanoid Hairy Soul Man hears a cry.

accessibilityAttributes.attributeSubType1IdDescription: Actively welcomes people with access needs.

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Offer multiple options for booking - web, email, phone
Offer a range of contact methods for receiving complaints
Train your staff in disability awareness
Have accessibility information and photos, including of a bathroom, room and/or floor plan on your website (can be emailed on request)
Ask all visitors if there are any specific needs to be met
Advise tour guides of the access needs of guests at the time of booking (includes pick up and drop off requirements)

attributeBlocks.attributeSubType2IdDescription: Welcomes and assists people who have challenges with learning, communication, understanding and behaviour. (includes people with autism, intellectual disability, Down syndrome, acquired brain injury (ABI), dyslexia and dementia)

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Train your staff in communicating with people with learning or behavioural challenges
Use Plain English / easy read signage and information (includes menus and emergency information)
A quiet space is available at the venue/ facility

attributeBlocks.attributeSubType2IdDescription: Caters for people who are blind or have vision loss.

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Have  Braille and tactile signage on all information and paths of travel
Use easy read fonts in your signage and communication materials (Helvetica and Arial)
Have raised tactile buttons in your lifts
Have handrails on all your stairways

attributeBlocks.attributeSubType2IdDescription: Caters for people who are deaf or have hearing loss.

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Train your staff in communicating with people who are deaf or have hearing loss
Have a low noise reception areas with hearing loss friendly acoustics and adequate lighting for viewing facial expressions (includes common areas which are free of background noise, background music)

attributeBlocks.attributeSubType2IdDescription: Caters for people with sufficient mobility to climb a few steps but who would benefit from fixtures to aid balance. (This includes people using walking frames and mobility aids)

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Use floors/coverings which are slip resistant, firm and smooth
Use non-slip tiles in the bathroom or slip resistant matting
Have grab rails in the bathroom
Provide seating in common areas including reception area

attributeBlocks.attributeSubType2IdDescription: Caters for people who use a wheelchair.

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Have step free outdoor pathways (includes picnic areas, barbecues and shelters)
Have a doorbell or intercom at an accessible height and display a contact number (accessible height is 900mm-1100 mm)
Have a step free main entrance to the building and/or reception area (includes ramps or slopes with a maximum gradient of 1:14, otherwise are too steep for wheelchairs)
Have step free access to restaurant, lounge and bar
Have step free access to the conference or function room
Have accessible seating areas in theatrette
Have lifts with enough space for people using a mobility aid to enter and turn around to use the lift buttons. Buttons are at accessible height.
Have doorways which are easy to open and have lever handles (doorways 850mm or wider when open and not heavy)
Have an accessible public toilet which is unlocked
Have a wheelchair accessible toilet / shower and change room
Have at least one wheelchair accessible parking space with wheelchair accessible signage clearly displayed (International standards are 3200mm wide x 2500 mm high)

attributeBlocks.attributeSubType2IdDescription: Caters for people with high support needs who travel with a support person.

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Have a bathroom which is fully accessible and equipped with ceiling hoist and adult change table
Have a Changing Places or Lift & Change toilet with a hoist and adult change table

attributeBlocks.attributeSubType2IdDescription: Caters for people with allergies and intolerances.

attributes.attributeIdDescription: Modify your cooking and cleaning practices to cater for people with food allergies or chemical intolerances (could include menus with meals free from: nuts, dairy, seafood, eggs, gluten etc)
Train your staff to respond to allergic reactions
Adhere to The Food Authority requirements for allergy management in food preparation

_source.productName: Majelen and JC and the Tree - Mt Nimmel Hall
_source.productDescription:
This December, two of Australia's most exciting independent actsâ€”Majelen and JC and the Treeâ€”join forces for an unforgettable East Coast tour.

Fresh off the release of her debut album Stuck With You, recorded at the iconic Abbey Road Studios, Majelen is quickly becoming one of Australia's most captivating new voices. Known for her percussive guitar style, raw vocal energy, and genre-bending acoustic sound, Majelen has spent 2025 touring with the Acoustic Guitar Spectacular and Mitch King, while living full-time on the road in her converted bus. Entirely self-managed and fiercely independent, she continues to carve her own path with honest storytelling and a DIY spirit that resonates deeply with audiences.

Sharing the stage is folk-rock fusion duo JC and the Tree, whose soaring violin melodies, earthy guitar tones, and heartfelt harmonies have inspired fans across Australia and beyond. Drawing from their Sunshine Coast roots, they create soundscapes that capture the beauty of nature and the connection between people and place. With performances at major festivals including Glastonbury, Splendour in the Grass, Bluesfest, and WOMAD, JC and the Tree bring a wealth of experience, passion, and authenticity to every show.

Together, Majelen and JC and the Tree promise an evening of powerful music, uplifting storytelling, and a celebration of artistry that is both intimate and unforgettable.

Come along to the special Wildflowering Women Artisan Market and EOY Party and help them celebrate the (almost) end of a great year at the Gallery.

Book your FREE ticket now!
